	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://allin.psu.edu/&quot;&gt;All In at Penn State: A Commitment to Diversity and Inclusion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

